- Night vision systems are categorized based on technology, with active IR systems, passive IR systems, and intelligent headlight systems being key drivers propelling market growth. Components like image sensors, displays, control units, and others are integral to the functioning of these systems, making them indispensable for passenger cars and commercial vehicles to improve visibility and prevent accidents.
