Regulatory focus on vehicle safety standards is a significant driver influencing market dynamics, leading to mandates requiring advanced driver-assistance systems like night vision and driver monitoring systems in vehicles to reduce road fatalities, enhance safety, and promote responsible driving behaviors. This regulatory push is compelling automakers to prioritize safety systems' integration, driving market growth and fostering technological advancements in the industry.

